e impact of\ndiffuse atmospheric background in daylight operation by means of spectral and\ntemporal filtering.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Sep 2021 17:28:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 13 Jan 2022 17:10:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-18"}
