nts an\noverview of state-of-the-art discussions on HRA, led by the Nuclear industry\ncommunity. It remarks that these discussions must be seriously considered in\ndefining a technical roadmap to a credible HRA method for the Oil and Gas\nindustry.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Sep 2021 23:25:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-30"}
