h that the Lie symmetries are satisfied. These symmetric\nBCJ numerators simultaneously satisfy the relabeling property of external lines\nand the algebraic properties (antisymmetry and Jacobi identity).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 Sep 2021 14:51:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 5 Jan 2022 13:50:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-16"}
